{"tid":45760,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我家大爺出街唔肯行","createTime":"2016-12-19T07:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T14:19:26.000Z","uid":40868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc198274ccb02fa5983ca2aa93a10005e80961c6","tid":45760,"uid":40868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:41:35.000Z","msg":"見我家大爺係屋企成日撩我地玩<br />\n就想帶佢出街消耗體力<br />\n問佢：街街好唔好呀<br />\n佢就笑曬口+條尾搖到就甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知放狗個陣死都唔肯行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常行幾步就坐係地下望住我<br />\n一係就嗲住要抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已經盡量搵d又靜又平既地比佢行架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4b9089e5dc9b0a20cbddc288abd53923443c45","tid":45760,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"好老？"},{"pid":"0141afa2709c91edd9edc9ff2fbd0a33eb7c25c9","tid":45760,"uid":40868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好老？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一歲都未夠"},{"pid":"52d2a16f09613a061d8889660083f8ce44f18206","tid":45760,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"影黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cce8106cfd78ce541fd3de2fc98773e44f0cece","tid":45760,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:58:47.000Z","msg":"柴？"},{"pid":"b013504f635229e1666a348babf0bb5ce5b15aa4","tid":45760,"uid":40868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柴？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n松鼠狗"},{"pid":"0020ea1b5aeed2084d9014cc598910847ecd11bd","tid":45760,"uid":40868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"<b